{"tid":1794257,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"酒店工會收120人申請","createTime":"2019-12-23T03:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T04:56:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"33c63579b6d1daa45f49d00be28d8e7d57f8a881","tid":1794257,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:49:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191223/KUC3P2ZKLWXUG5QDBOIMER6PJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191223%2FKUC3P2ZKLWXUG5QDBOIMER6PJU%2F&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwVTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=b4712a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191223%2FKUC3P2ZKLWXUG5QDBOIMER6PJU%2F&h=aa8d521f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191223/KUC3P2ZKLWXUG5QDBOIMER6PJU/</a><br />\n<br />\n酒店工會收120人申請<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191223/large/1577033970_3217.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191223%2Flarge%2F1577033970_3217.gif&h=1929f83a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港酒店工會昨在中環設街站招收會員。董立華攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】隨反修例風波持續，各行各業人士紛紛響應呼籲成立工會以籌備罷工及強攻特首及立法會選舉的選委會。新成立的香港酒店工會昨在愛丁堡廣場設立街站，向公眾介紹工會並即席招收會員。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：千人撐維族 「再教育營遲早在港出現」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關注催淚煙污染問題<br />\n<br />\n香港酒店工會主席徐先生稱工會約一個月前成立，暫時收到近120個申請，有20宗處理中。他指酒店工會主要是因應反送中運動而成立，希望團結同業聲音。現時同業面對不公義的政權，令人反思到各行業都面對不公制度、無理對待及福利問題。徐先生認為酒店業在此次反修例風波非獨善其身，警方在各區催淚彈放題，波及到不少酒店及商業大樓，各機構有否正視催淚彈污染通風系統等會直接影響員工及顧客安全，希望工會能監察及迫使各公司明確解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n近日不少工會以發動罷工為成立的其中一個目的，徐則指設立工會只是初期起步的階段，認為發動罷工仍是較為遙遠的事。他直指公眾對工會的文化及運作認識不深，對罷工仍存有很多憂慮，擔心會受公司清算、秋後算賬，「喺未徹底解決到同業嘅憂慮之前，我哋都唔會貿貿然發動罷工」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者凌懿君"},{"pid":"ef068fc43c65cfaa1229aeaeb250e9a2de8e3085","tid":1794257,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgwZ4tD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgwZ4tD.jpg&h=52b479a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGepv8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGepv8D.jpg&h=265d7544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocgLfAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocgLfAm.jpg&h=e2a8e121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cea8b31c9e50968298feb57c07ce89a0ede803e1","tid":1794257,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">和你坐  Stuck稅局</span><br />\n12月23日 星期一<br />\n時間 : 12:00<br />\n地點 : 稅務大樓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">稅局聖誕激光燈飾之夜</span><br />\n19:00<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「星火不息 燃點國際」集會</span><br />\n日期︰2019年12月23日(一)<br />\n時間︰晚上七時至九時<br />\n地點︰中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n主辦方︰張崑陽、候任中西區區議員梁晃維、民間集會團隊<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲警方發出不反對通知書</span>"},{"pid":"ba2b69abaae7b466e9d324a9895411ab6642df49","tid":1794257,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:54:27.000Z","msg":"得120個申請？酒店業冇咁少人㗎窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb95e4928070691eb0c173dad7c9f3ef319dc81","tid":1794257,"uid":159818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"酒店業係藍絲集中營黎，估都估到，生意差又會炒人。做酒店都黃既話通常果d都係深黃黎<br />\n利伸:酒店佬"},{"pid":"b4556632097d605a59d4fff8f1e247f91d2a5963","tid":1794257,"uid":272603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新德國聯署</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國聯邦議院《全球馬格尼茨基法案》</span></div><br />\n<div 